title: Disavowed (Restored)
description:
Issues 1-6 of 'Disavowed'

Homage Comics/DC Comics, 2000,

Written by Brandon Choi, Michael Heisler

Penciled and Inked by Tommy Lee Edwards, John Lucas 

Colored by Melissa Edwards

Like his law-enforcer father and grandfather before him, FBI Special Agent Dalton Morrell has a remarkable gift: he possesses the memories of his ancestors. Now Dalton joins others with gifts of their own in a common cause - saving the world from a mysterious, chillingly malevolent force.
